    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>Dominator Idle mixes clicker games with strategy. The controls are very simple just using your left mouse button to click!<br><br>Train troops and unlock magical upgrades in the associated panels.<br><br>Troops are your main battle strength and should be the forefront of gaining more battle power.<br><br>Magical upgrades will enhance your units in battle. <br><br>Troops first, magic second.<br><br>Engage in world conquest to take over all of Earth through these battles.<br><br>Once you have taken all of the territories of earth on the attack page, prestige in order to increase your overall strength!<br><br>This will reset upgrades but give you a permanent boost to your account! The enemies you face will be more challenging but with your newfound prestige they will be no match for you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer Notes</h2><br>I am a solo developer of the game and will be keeping it free forever.<br><br>More content releases are planned in the future such as cutscenes and more upgrades. <br><br>Currently in early access as there is a lot that needs improving such as a balance pass, sound, art, ui etc.<br><br>I hope you all enjoy playing the game and I appreciate your feedback!<br><br>Discord Server: ",
